{"tid":1228510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，共勉之","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:32:43.000Z","uid":163960,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"91b86a6c7c4f48688044823c61b82e7264bd8027","tid":1228510,"uid":163960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲要振作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白咁多位知道義士消息之後難免會唔開心、甚至有人萌生想自殺既念頭<br />\n但我地唔可以認輸，呢場抗爭仲有好長遠既路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歷年來，幾乎無一場抗爭係可以短時間內見到成效<br />\n我地一定要堅強，堅持到最後一刻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家請多啲關心身邊既人</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>多你一個真係好多</strong></span></span><br />\n如果想搵人傾訴，我係絕對絕對唔介意聽你講<br />\n咁多位巴絲，我地要頂硬上<br />\n關關難過關關過，唔可以辜負呢位義士既心血<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認清目標，堅持就是勝利</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n講到呢到，我有個諗法，不如開一個Tg群，散播下正能量，互相支持同鼓勵？"},{"pid":"29343a678d20454803aca18b3c3fdacc2890d8c1","tid":1228510,"uid":163960,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外，聽日會試下搞個free hug</span></span></strong><br />\n我知作用唔大，但好希望透過呢個小小既擁抱去鼓勵大家"},{"pid":"e3f67093cc75834a83d60f2036e5b0b2367e88c5","tid":1228510,"uid":163960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b704f407cf09bd317a18fa7246aa3f35ff836e7e","tid":1228510,"uid":159997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"qu